"tid":508803,"uid":78483,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:15:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>信教咪Christmas,唔信咪Xmas<br />\n<br />\nNot X'mas</blockquote>Xmas個X就係基督<span style=\"color: red;\">Christ</span>既希臘文&Chi;&rho;&iota;&sigma;&tau;o&sigmaf;<br />\n<br />\n關信唔信教咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前（天主教）小學聽過老師話 Xmas 刪左christ（耶穌，是對耶穌唔尊敬，叫我地寫聖誕卡唔好用Xmas"},{"pid":"a1e54f481f2d72d6c04d6caf29ff6cdfc27dd1d8","tid":508803,"uid":5150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cd407749ed55558fe6ec0987fb7e76ef0252e85","tid":508803,"uid":78483,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:15:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>信教咪Christmas,唔信咪Xmas<br />\n<br />\nNot X'mas</blockquote>Xmas個X就係基督<span style=\"color: red;\">Christ</span>既希臘文&Chi;&rho;&iota;&sigma;&tau;o&sigmaf;<br />\n<br />\n關信唔信教咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前（天主教）小學聽過老師話 Xmas 刪左christ（耶穌，是對耶穌唔尊敬，叫我地寫聖誕卡唔好用Xmas"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T06:42:03.000Z","msg":"教畜嘅嘢信一成都多啦<br />\n<br />\n&Chi;&Rho;&Iota;&Sigma;&Tau;&Omicron;&Sigma; = Christ<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chi_Rho\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FChi_Rho&d=HL%2FrXwgy5U97G3dfGkx76DCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=cf057d95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chi_Rho</a><br />\n<br />\nChi or X is often used to abbreviate the name Christ, as in the holiday Christmas (Xmas). <br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chi_(letter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FChi_%28letter&d=HL%2FrXwgy5U97G3dfGkx76DCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=f80649a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chi_(letter</a>)#Symbolism"}]}